reviewText: I love to surprise the kids with a video, they love getting something in the mail, they saw the very first movie but didn't own it and hadnt seen the second one , when I saw the first and second movie at such a fantastic price I knew I had to order it for them, great deal
Title: Nanny McPhee / Nanny McPhee Returns

reviewText: Well, with this two movie series, I haven't had a chance to see the first movie yet.  I saw the second movie already on one of the movie channels.  I really enjoyed it and they seem to be a good choice for families to gather round the tv for family time to watch and talk about at the end.
Title: Nanny McPhee / Nanny McPhee Returns

reviewText: Our family loves both of these movies and it was great to find them together. We like the first but LOVE the second.
Title: Nanny McPhee / Nanny McPhee Returns

reviewText: No doubt the creater's of  these films has a wild imagination, but that aside; it is good, clean fun that adults and kids alike can enjoy without fear of excessivie sex & violence.
Title: Nanny McPhee / Nanny McPhee Returns

reviewText: these are great movies for the family to see. children will love these. thanks
Title: Nanny McPhee / Nanny McPhee Returns

reviewText: Not only are these movies entertaining, they also teach a lesson.  I have watched them both more than once with my great-niece and she has gotten something from the films each time.  Manners, respect and caring.  Wonderful family films.
Title: Nanny McPhee / Nanny McPhee Returns
